Subject: Re: [T2] 72 Disc vs 73 up?????

The '72 brakes were also used in '71 making them a two year only part.  The 
spindles, calipers, and rotors are all different from the '73 to '79 parts.  
The rotors and calipers are larger than the '71-'72.

